OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPeriods of rain initially,
OL,6,Fperhaps turning heavy, combining with
OL,7,Fgales to bring decidedly un-Spring
OL,8,Flike weather. Clearing to blustery
OL,9,Fshowers late morning, with outbreaks
OL,10,Foccasional in west, isolated with best
OL,11,Fof brightness in east. Showers turning
OL,12,Fwintry across higher ground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers pushing across the
OL,15,Farea on strong west to southwest
OL,16,Fwinds. Outbreaks ranging from
OL,17,Foccasional in Moray and isolated
OL,18,Faround the east coasts, also turning
OL,19,Fwintry to quite low levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
